NAME
       fromgif - convert a GIF image into an IRIS image

SYNOPSIS
       fromgif inimage.gif outimage.rgb

DESCRIPTION
       fromgif  converts  a  Compuserve  GIF image file into an
       IRIS image file.

SEE ALSO
       togif(6D)
